Text: "Thousands of people flock to Digha every month to take a break from the chaos\
  \ of city life. It is a common beach in India.However, most stay confined to the\
  \ beaches and it is the beach which is under development. However, there is fishing\
  \ villages near by which is \u201Cmost beautiful village in the world.\u201D\n\n\
  There is Digha Mohona International Fish market,with relishable tastes and variety\
  \ of fishes.. small tola in the seashores will greet you with awesome tasty fishes\
  \ that will leave you awestruck. The seabeach has increadble serene environment\
  \ all around  and is definitely worth a visit...."
